    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    AddOns
    Represents additional toppings/add-ons that can be included with menu items.
    Beverage
    Represents a beverage menu item with size and flavor options.
    BeverageController
    Controller class for handling beverage selection and ordering functionality.
    Bread
    Represents available bread types for sandwiches and other menu items.
    Burger
    Represents a Burger MenuItem that extends Sandwich.
    BurgerController
    The BurgerController class manages the user interface for customizing a burger.
    BurgerTest
    A test class for verifying the functionality and pricing of the Burger class.
    CartController
    Controller class for managing the shopping cart functionality.
    Combo
    Represents a combo meal consisting of a sandwich, beverage, and side.
    ComboController
    The ComboController class handles user interactions for creating and ordering a combo meal.
    Flavor
    Represents available flavor options for beverages and other menu items.
    Main
     
    MainController
    Main controller class for handling navigation between different views in the application.
    MenuItem
    Abstract class that represents a food/beverage item in our restaurant
    Order
    The Order class holds a number to uniquely identify each order and an ArrayList of MenuItems that represent the food/beverage the user wants to order.
    OrderController
    The OrderController class manages the user interface for viewing and managing orders.
    Protein
    Represents available protein options for menu items.
    Sandwich
    Represents a Sandwich MenuItem with bread, protein, and optional add-ons.
    SandwichController
    The SandwichController class manages the user interface for customizing sandwiches.
    SandwichTest
    A test class for verifying the functionality and pricing of Sandwich.
    Side
    Represents side dish options available for meals.
    Sides
    Represents a side dish menu item with customizable size and quantity.
    SidesController
    This class controls the "Sides" view in the application, managing user input for sides, size, quantity, and price.
    Size
    Represents available size options for menu items.
